枚举类 Debug

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<Debug>
ltseed.chatinmc.Utils.Debug
所有已实现的接口:
Serializable, Comparable<Debug>, Constable
public enum Debug extends Enum<Debug>
An enum representing different levels of debug output, including A, B, and N (none). Each enum constant has methods for outputting information, warnings, and errors at its respective level. Additionally, there are methods for debugging at levels A and B.
版本:
1.0
作者:
ltseed
